ank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fnote-seconds-schole-compilation%252Fid376201016%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Note of Seconds -schole Compilation vol.2-Various Artists']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/a-rosa-e-o-girassol.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/arosa.jpg" alt="A Rosa e O Girassol / A Rosa e O Girassol" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/a-rosa-e-o-girassol.php">A Rosa e O Girassol<br />A Rosa e O Girassol</a></h4><p>海で聴きたくなる、落ち着いた雰囲気のブラジリアンアルバム。アコースティック中心でお酒を飲みながらゆったりとした時間を過ごしましょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003K945Q8?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003K945Q8" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'A Rosa e O Girassol-A Rosa e O Girassol']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fa-rosa-e-o-girassol%252Fid374477380%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'A Rosa e O Girassol-A Rosa e O Girassol']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/remembering-tomorrow.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/remebering.jpg" alt="Remembering Tomorrow / Steve Kuhn" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/remembering-tomorrow.php">Remembering Tomorrow<br />Steve Kuhn</a></h4><p>とても