.jp/review/upload/longdistance.jpg" alt="Long Distance / Onra" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/long-distance.php">Long Distance<br />Onra</a></h4><p>ファンキーでいて重みのあるビートが中心の音楽です。エレクトロニカなどの影響も感じられる作品です。夜の海で大きな音で聴きたくなります。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003F10ZWE?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003F10ZWE" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Long Distance-Onra']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Flong-distance%252Fid371341181%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Long Distance-Onra']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/nympheas.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/nympheas.jpg" alt="Nympheas / a-fei" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/nympheas.php">Nympheas<br />a-fei</a></h4><p>生楽器＋エレクトロニックな作品。静かな音に粘りのあるリズムが特徴の音楽です。海にいるときに聴くと不思議と落ち着ける作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0018OFGY2?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0018OFGY2" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Nympheas-a-fei']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fnympheas%252Fid281765936%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Nympheas-a-fei']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

